--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DESCRIPTION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This role manages python_crypto.

Python-crypto is a collection of both secure hash functions (such as MD5 and
SHA), and various encryption algorithms (AES, DES, RSA, ElGamal, etc.).

For more detailed information on the usage and available configuration options
please consult the following sections.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
USAGE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

INSTALL
  - hosts: all
    roles:
     - role: python_crypto
       python_crypto_state: 'install'

REMOVE
  - hosts: all
    roles:
     - role: python_crypto
       python_crypto_state: 'remove'

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VARIABLES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ROLE
  python_crypto_state
    Specify predetermined 'python_crypto_state' variable (string).

    Install: 'true' | 'yes' | 'install'
    Remove : 'false' | 'no' | 'remove'
    Default: 'install'

